	body
		// 960px site container 
		.site-container
			
			// header and logo for questionnaire 
			.qaire-header
				a.lz-logo(href='#') LegalZoom
				h1 Creating Your LLC
			
			// steps nav 
			ul.steps-solid
				li.completed
					a
						span.link About your business
						span.arrow
				li.completed
					a
						span.link Name & address
						span.arrow
				li.completed
					a
						span.link Owners & Mgmt
						span.arrow
				li.active
					a
						span.link Tax setup
						span.arrow
				li.inactive
					a
						span.link Business setup
						span.arrow
				li.inactive.last
					a
						span.link Place order
						span.arrow
			.clear
			
			// main content 
			.content-main
				h1 Now, on to your business tax setup
				p
					| We can help your business get a federal tax identification number as well as a consultation on best practices to maximize your tax savings.
				h3 Do you want help getting a federal tax ID (EIN)?
				p
					| Most businesses are required to obtain a federal tax identification number (also known as an EIN) from the IRS. This number is used when filing tax returns, opening business bank accounts, or paying employees (if applicable). Additionally, an EIN keeps your personal social security number private in business transactions.
				p
					| We can do all of the work to obtain the tax identification number for you or just prepare your paperwork for you to file yourself. (
					a#help_ein.help see fee details
					| ).
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#ein_01(checked='checked', name='ein', type='radio')
						label(for='ein_01') Yes, please obtain a tax identification number for my business
					.form-fields
						input#ein_02(name='ein', type='radio')
						label(for='ein_02') Yes, please prepare the paperwork and I will file on my own
					.form-fields
						input#ein_03(name='ein', type='radio')
						label(for='ein_03') No
					a#help_ein_answer.help.icon.lz-icon-help.orange.small.desc
						| How did most people answer this question?
				h3 Do you want a free consultation on reducing your taxes?
				p
					| Taxes can be one of the biggest expenses for your business every year. We have partnered with Corporate Tax Network to provide a webinar and a free consultation with a tax professional focused on reducing tax expenses for your business ($199 value). To learn more, 
					a#help_ctn.help click here
					| .
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#ctn_01(checked='checked', name='ctn', type='radio')
						label(for='ctn_01') Yes, I would like to learn about reducing my tax expenses
					.form-fields
						input#ctn_02(name='ctn', type='radio')
						label(for='ctn_02') No thanks
				hr.top-space
				
				// page navigation 
				ul.page-nav
					li
						a.link-back(href='qaire-13.html')
							i.icon.lz-icon-blue.arrow-back
							span Back
					li
						// orange button with icon on right 
						a.button.orange.flex.has-right(href='qaire-16.html')
							span.button-right
								span.inner
									i.icon.button-icon.arrow-large
							span.button-center Save & continue
				.clear
				br
				br
			
			// sidebar 
			.content-sidebar
				.qaire-sidebar
					.customer-service
					blockquote
						.open &#8220;
						p.quote
							| Excellent experience. Very smooth and extremely reasonable on the cost.
							span.close  &#8221; 
						.from - Creed N., Tuscola, TX
			.clear
		
