				| . LegalZoom.com, Inc., 101 N Brand Blvd, 11th Floor, Glendale, CA 91203 is a registered and bonded legal document assistant, #0104, Los Angeles County (exp. 12/13).
		
		// tooltip container 
		.tooltip-container
			#help_ein_tooltip.tooltip.wide
				.arrow.left
				.close
					i.icon.icon-tooltip-close
				p
					| Over 70% of our customers choose to have LegalZoom obtain an EIN for their business. A much smaller number choose to have us complete their paperwork so they can file it with the IRS on your own. The fee of each option is based on the package you select at checkout.
				p Our fee to obtain a tax identification for your business:
				ul
					li $49 with the Express Gold package
					li $79 with the Economy or Standard package
				p Our fee to create the paperwork for your business:
				ul
					li Included with the Express Gold package
					li $30 with the Economy or Standard package
				p
					| If you have more questions about business owners, please call us at (855) 773-0880.
			#help_ein_answer_tooltip.tooltip
				.arrow.left
				.close
					i.icon.icon-tooltip-close
				p Our customers answered...
				p
					| Yes, obtain tax identification - 76%
					br
					| Yes, prepare the IRS form only - 6%
					br
					| No - 21%
				p Based on a sample of more than 40,000 LLC customers in 2013.
			#help_ctn_tooltip.tooltip.wide
				.arrow.left
				.close
					i.icon.icon-tooltip-close
				p During your free one hour webinar and consultation, you'll learn:
				ul
					li How your business is taxed
					li How to stay in compliance with IRS requirements
					li Recent tax law changes that affect your business
					li Commonly missed deductions
					li The right way to pay yourself
					li What happens when you have a loss or profit
					li Using proper bank accounts
					li Tax strategies of the wealthy
					li And more
				p
					| The tax information can save you time and money. There's no risk or obligation on your part to continue to use the service after the free webinar and consultation. If you have more questions about business owners, please call us at (855) 773-0880.
		
